And?

204
00:06:29,301 --> 00:06:30,912
I don't know.
I mean...

205
00:06:30,955 --> 00:06:34,002
a lot's happened since
we started out together.

206
00:06:34,045 --> 00:06:36,134
I knew my TO would be
important to my career,

207
00:06:36,178 --> 00:06:38,441
