293
00:09:21,561 --> 00:09:24,346
Out buying drugs,
if he has any money.

294
00:09:24,389 --> 00:09:25,826
And if he's not?

295
00:09:25,869 --> 00:09:27,958
Jared will do anything
to get a fix,

296
00:09:28,002 --> 00:09:30,526
including selling our baby.

297
00:09:30,570 --> 00:09:31,788
[ Helicopter blades whirring ]

298
00:09:34,225 --> 00:09:35,662
Gold pickup,
two blocks up.

299
00:09:35,705 --> 00:09:36,619
[ Tires squealing,
engine revving ]

300
00:09:36,663 --> 00:09:40,362
♪♪

301
00:09:40,405 --> 00:09:42,582
Negative.
Texas plates.

302
00:09:43,974 --> 00:09:45,193
Five hours old.

303
00:09:45,236 --> 00:09:46,760
That poor mother must begoing out of her mind.

304
00:09:48,805 --> 00:09:49,850
Let me guess --

305
00:09:49,893 --> 00:09:51,329
you think if the parents
had properly

