I can't see
around the truck.

371
00:11:58,456 --> 00:11:59,631
Move it!
I got it.

372
00:11:59,675 --> 00:12:00,807
Move! Hey!I got it after this car.

373
00:12:00,850 --> 00:12:02,983
Hold on. There we go.Got it.

374
00:12:05,420 --> 00:12:07,465
Do you see him?No.

375
00:12:07,509 --> 00:12:09,816
Well, maybe -- maybe he turned
around when we got stuck.

376
00:12:09,859 --> 00:12:11,469
7-Adam-19,
we've lost visual.

