00:13:51,004 --> 00:13:52,135
once we get her back.

422
00:13:53,310 --> 00:13:54,355
Ifwe get her back.

423
00:13:54,398 --> 00:13:56,357
[ Radio chatter ]

424
00:13:56,400 --> 00:13:58,750
You know, whenever you need
Halloween costumes

425
00:13:58,794 --> 00:14:00,230
for Lopez Jr.,

