439
00:14:29,303 --> 00:14:31,087
Lot of long hours.

440
00:14:31,131 --> 00:14:32,306
But you were close.

441
00:14:32,349 --> 00:14:33,960
Yeah, eventually.

442
00:14:34,003 --> 00:14:36,919
